<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delete Account</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/main/BookHub-logo-mini.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style-for-all.css">
</head>

<body>

    <%- include("../partials/navbar") %>

        <p>We're sad to see you go, but we hope your next adventure is amazing! Our digital door is always unlocked for you.</p>
        
        
        <p>Are you sure you want to delete your account?</p>

        <form action="/dashboard/<%=user._id%>/delete?_method=PUT" method="POST">
            <button>Delete</button>
        </form>

        <a href="/">...or Return to BookHub 📖✨</a>

</body>

</html>